high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the cardboard toilet paper tube off of the toilet paper holder attached to the counter in front of you.
Turn around and take two steps forward, then turn back around and look straight ahead.
Put the cardboard tube on top of the toilet tank on the left side.
Turn left and walk over to the door, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the toilet paper roll off of the counter.
Turn right and walk back over to the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put two toilet paper rolls on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the trash can.
Pick up the toilet paper roll off of the holder.
Go to the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on the back of the toilet.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Pick up the toilet paper roll on the left of the sink.
Go back to the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on the back of the toilet on the right side of the other roll.
anns.task_desc: Put two toilet paper rolls on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the trash can
Grab the cardboard tube out of the trash can
Back up and look at the toilet
Put the tube on top of the toilet
Turn left and go to the left of the sink
Grab the toilet paper off of the counter
Turn right and go to the toilet
Put the toilet paper on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Putting a cardboard tube and toilet paper on top of the toilet
